//appcenter click
1. npm run build
2. sync the project to update build folder
3. run script on terminal at root project 
ios:
appcenter codepush release -a MotivesVN/M-System-3 -c ios/App/App/public -t 2.9 -d Production -m --description "Change public folder to public rename old puclic folder"
android:
appcenter codepush release -a MotivesVN/M-System-Android -c android/app/src/main/assets/public/ --target-binary-version "3.7" -d Production -m --description "Lorem"

4. Restart and open the app again
5. Checking the update devices
appcenter codepush deployment history Production --app MotivesVN/M-System-Android

config if change the couputer need to update node module for codepush:
https://github.com/mapiacompany/capacitor-codepush/pull/77/files#diff-6f00ee27b1215ca9a6e02213e5f498e2eda6821fe35296ed2ca8191251a00ecd

specification
 Nodejs: v16.17.0   (LTS: Gallium)
clear development
appcenter codepush deployment clear -a MotivesVN/M-System-Android Production


